  NOTE -->|expands control scope into| CONTROL
  NOTE -->|expands ingress scope into| INGRESS
  NOTE -->|expands RTDL scope into| RTDL
  NOTE -->|expands case/label scope into| CASELABEL
  NOTE -->|expands learning scope into| LEARNING
  NOTE -->|expands ops/governance scope into| OPSGOV

  GHA -->|authenticates through| OIDC
  GHA -->|dispatches bounded orchestration to| SFN
  SFN -->|pins run identity in| RUNID
  SFN -->|writes proof receipts to| RCPT
  RCPT -->|supports later reconstruction in| RECON
  SFN -->|publishes control signals to| CTRLBUS
  CTRLBUS -->|rides control transport on| MSK

  OBJ -->|supplies replay source world to| REPLAY
  REPLAY -->|materializes bounded replay for| WSP
  RUNID -->|scopes replay activity for| WSP
  RUNID -->|scopes ingress access-log truth for| APIGW
  RUNID -->|scopes RTDL intake truth for| RINTAKE
  RUNID -->|scopes dataset admission truth for| DSADMIT
  RUNID -->|scopes later evidence challenge for| RECON
  WSP -->|pushes bounded ingress load to| APIGW
  APIGW -->|invokes ingress function at| IGINVOKE
  IGINVOKE -->|checks idempotency in| IGDEDUPE
  IGINVOKE -->|routes failed-closed outcomes to| IGFAIL
  IGDEDUPE -->|hands admitted traffic to| IGPUBLISH
  IGPUBLISH -->|publishes fraud traffic to| TTRAFFIC
  TTRAFFIC -->|rides traffic transport on| MSK
  GLUE -. schema boundary .-> TTRAFFIC

  TTRAFFIC -->|feeds admitted fraud traffic into| RINTAKE
  RINTAKE -->|derives arrival-event projection in| APROJ
  RINTAKE -->|derives arrival-entity projection in| EPROJ
  RINTAKE -->|derives flow-anchor projection in| FPROJ
  APROJ -->|publishes arrival-events context to| TCTXA
  EPROJ -->|publishes arrival-entities context to| TCTXE
  FPROJ -->|publishes fraud-flow anchors to| TFLOW
  TCTXA -->|supplies projected arrival events to| CSFB
  TCTXE -->|supplies projected arrival entities to| CSFB
  TFLOW -->|supplies projected flow anchors to| CSFB
  GLUE -. schema boundary .-> TCTXA
  GLUE -. schema boundary .-> TCTXE
  GLUE -. schema boundary .-> TFLOW
  CSFB -->|binds resolved context for| IEG
  IEG -->|supplies entity/graph truth to| OFP
  OFP -->|requests active-bundle policy through| BUNDLE
  BUNDLE -->|hands governed bundle truth to| DFGUARD
  DFGUARD -->|permits decision formation in| DECIDE
  DECIDE -->|publishes decision outcome through| DLPUB
  DLPUB -->|emits action intent through| ALINTENT
  ALINTENT -->|commits action outcomes in| ALOUTCOME
  ALOUTCOME -->|appends continuity truth to| DLA
  DLPUB -->|appends archive evidence to| ARCH
  DLPUB -->|publishes decision/archive stream to| TDEC
  ALOUTCOME -->|emits case-worthy outcome into| CTRIG

  CTRIG -->|opens or reuses case through| COPEN
  COPEN -->|commits append-only case truth in| CTIMELINE
  CTIMELINE -->|submits candidate labels to| LADM
  LADM -->|commits authoritative supervision in| LTRUTH

  DLA -->|contributes runtime decision evidence to| DSADMIT
  CTIMELINE -->|contributes case-timeline evidence to| DSADMIT
  LTRUTH -->|contributes supervision truth to| DSADMIT
  DSADMIT -->|admits bounded learning slice into| OFSBUILD
  OFSBUILD -->|hands dataset basis to| OFSQUAL
  OFSQUAL -->|releases leakage-safe basis to| TRAIN
  TRAIN -->|commits managed train/eval results into| LINEAGE
  LINEAGE -->|submits governed candidate to| PROMOTE
  PROMOTE -->|publishes active-bundle truth in| ABUNDLE
  ABUNDLE -->|resolves active runtime bundle for| BUNDLE

  RCPT -->|stores receipt evidence in| EVID
  RECON -->|reads and challenges evidence in| EVID
  IGFAIL -->|stores fail-closed evidence in| EVID
  DLA -->|stores decision continuity evidence in| EVID
  ARCH -->|stores archive evidence in| EVID
  CTIMELINE -->|stores case evidence in| EVID
  LTRUTH -->|stores label truth evidence in| EVID
  OFSQUAL -->|stores dataset-quality evidence in| EVID
  TRAIN -->|stores train/eval evidence in| EVID
  PROMOTE -->|stores promotion/rollback evidence in| EVID

  IGINVOKE -->|reads active handles from| SSM
  WSP -->|reads replay handles from| SSM
  BUNDLE -->|reads active bundle handles from| SSM
  TRAIN -->|reads bounded learning basis from| OBJ
  OFSBUILD -->|reads admitted source world from| OBJ
  REPLAY -->|reads promoted replay world from| OBJ

  APIGW -->|emits edge metrics and logs to| CW
  IGINVOKE -->|emits ingress telemetry to| CW
  WSP -->|emits replay telemetry to| CW
  CSFB -->|emits context-binding telemetry to| CW
  IEG -->|emits graph-resolution telemetry to| CW
  OFP -->|emits feature-plane telemetry to| CW
  DFGUARD -->|emits decision-guard telemetry to| CW
  DECIDE -->|emits decision telemetry to| CW
  ALOUTCOME -->|emits action telemetry to| CW
  CTIMELINE -->|emits case telemetry to| CW
  LTRUTH -->|emits label telemetry to| CW
  OFSQUAL -->|emits dataset-quality telemetry to| CW
  TRAIN -->|emits managed-learning telemetry to| CW
  LINEAGE -->|emits lineage/promote telemetry to| CW
  RECON -->|emits reconstruction telemetry to| CW

  CW -->|feeds live operator view in| OPSVIEW
  OPSVIEW -->|materializes alert state in| ALERT
  EVID -->|supports evidence challenge in| DRIFT
  ABUNDLE -->|supports active-bundle challenge in| DRIFT
  RCPT -->|supports receipt challenge in| DRIFT
  ALERT -->|routes alert response into| RUNBOOK
  DRIFT -->|routes drift response into| RUNBOOK
  OPSVIEW -->|surfaces idle/cost posture in| COST
  COST -->|routes cost-control action into| RUNBOOK
  RUNBOOK -->|returns governed bundle control to| BUNDLE
  RUNBOOK -->|returns governed case control to| CTIMELINE

